	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- How bad is (legal terms) to put screenshots from emulated NES games into a website? Would I violate some copyright after all, assuming the images are not doctored?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
