	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't think it's a problem, as there are many, many sites with game screenshots.  Trademark violation is possible, but even that seems more remote (more like using a trademarked character on the site's logo, or for endorsing something).
<br />
<br />I'm no lawyer, but I guess it couldn't hurt to have a notice like "All copyrighted images and trademarks are properties of their respective owners".

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


